videos.headline: Oregon's Herbert connects with Redd for 18-yard TD
videos.description: Justin Herbert executes a successful 18-yard touchdown pass to Jaylon Redd to put Oregon on the board.

videos.headline: Herbert's second TD pass pads Oregon's lead
videos.description: Justin Herbert completes a throw to Tabari Hines for a 9-yard Oregon touchdown.

videos.headline: Oregon's Dillon fights through the defense for 20-yard TD
videos.description: Justin Herbert connects with Kano Dillon, who fights off Portland State's defense for a  20-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Portland State gets on the board with 71-yd TD
videos.description: Portland State's Charlie Taumoepeau finds an opening and scores a 71-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Oregon's Habibi-Likio runs the ball in for a quick TD
videos.description: Cyrus Habibi-Likio squeezes into the end zone for a 1-yard Oregon touchdown.

videos.headline: Herbert finds Johnson for 11-yard Oregon TD
videos.description: Justin Herbert connects with Johnny Johnson III for an 11-yard Oregon touchdown.

videos.headline: Brooks-James delivers on a 1-yd Oregon TD
videos.description: Oregon's Tony Brooks-James increases the lead with a 1-yd rushing touchdown.
